column5: Looking for anyone that might have information on walleye success below the dam at Lac Seul during the last week in May and the end of June. Are the walleye at the dam area yet in late May and do they move away from the dam area by the end of June? Or do the walleye pretty much stay in the dam area all the time? I have fished below the dam usually no more than 1/2 to 3/4 of a mile away from the dam in early June. thanks in advance, Pete
